lyrics:
[Verse]
I gave my heart, I gave my soul
But now she's gone, I've lost control
Her love slipped through my trembling hands
Now I'm left in a desolate land

[Chorus]
Lost in the echoes of a love long gone
My heart screams out, a battle rages on
I'm drowning in the tears that I can't contain
In this punk rock ballad of heartache and pain
